        "3073": {
          "vnum": 3073,
          "name": "A Cozy Stone Cottage",
          "description": "The room here opens up with enough space to house fifty inhabitants. In the center of the room is a large table set with platefuls of delicious looking cakes and two steaming soup bowls. Along the walls, shelves house many meticulously arranged jars and specimens. Axes and other foresting tools rest neatly upon a rack in the corner of the room.",
          "grid_x": 0,
          "grid_y": 1,
          "exits": {
            "n": {
              "to_vnum": 3072,
              "to_zone": "Forest of Evermore",
              "to_room_name": "Before a Stone Cottage",
              "direction": "n",
              "is_cross_zone": false,
              "is_portal": false
            }
          },
          "npcs": [
            {
              "name": "Aiel",
              "description": "Having worked hard all day Aiel the caretakers' wife stands here sweating profusely. Yet in all of her daily labors she retains a beauty and nobility that leaves you envious of the recipient of her affections.",
              "unique": true
            },
            {
              "name": "Almezar",
              "description": "Charged with protecting the forest, Almezar has been working here for all of his life and loves it dearly. He has sworn to uphold the purity and sanctity of the life in this wood, he views it as his duty and honor to Isvaelin.",
              "unique": true
            }
          ]
        },
        "3074": {
          "vnum": 3074,
          "name": "The Forest of Evermore",
          "description": "Pine needles rain down upon the trail as the wind rustles through tree the branches. Mosses grow on some of the trees while insects burrow into the pines, making their homes. The trail continues to the west, as well as south towards a small stone cottage.",
          "grid_x": 0,
          "grid_y": -1,
          "exits": {
            "w": {
              "to_vnum": 3075,
              "to_zone": "Forest of Evermore",
              "to_room_name": "The Forest of Evermore",
              "direction": "w",
              "is_cross_zone": false,
              "is_portal": false
            }
          },
          "npcs": []
        },
        "3075": {
          "vnum": 3075,
          "name": "The Forest of Evermore",
          "description": "You come to another intersection of trails between the massive pines. Leading off in several different directions, the paths are swept clear of any large debris. Each path is clearly well defined by small blue stones that mark the edges along each path.",
          "grid_x": -1,
          "grid_y": -1,
          "exits": {
            "n": {
              "to_vnum": 3076,
              "to_zone": "Forest of Evermore",
              "to_room_name": "The Forest of Evermore",
              "direction": "n",
              "is_cross_zone": false,
              "is_portal": false
            }
          },
          "npcs": []
        },
        "3076": {
          "vnum": 3076,
          "name": "The Forest of Evermore",
          "description": "As you proceed through the forest you stumble upon a small stream. Flowing quietly through the wood, the stream is frequented by all of the local forest life. The rustle of pines and the trickle of the stream are quite soothing.",
          "grid_x": -1,
          "grid_y": -2,
          "exits": {
            "w": {
              "to_vnum": 3077,
              "to_zone": "Forest of Evermore",
              "to_room_name": "The Forest of Evermore",
              "direction": "w",
              "is_cross_zone": false,
              "is_portal": false
            }
          },
          "npcs": [
            {
              "name": "Faerie Queen",
              "description": "The faerie is scintillatingly beautiful; she flits about energetically attempting to avoid your gaze.  You have found the elusive faerie queen.",
              "unique": true
            },
            {
              "name": "Faerie guard",
              "description": "The faerie guard looks big and intimidating, at least for a faerie anyways.",
              "unique": true
            }
          ]
        },
        "3077": {
          "vnum": 3077,
          "name": "The Forest of Evermore",
          "description": "The colossal pines reach far up into the heavens as if they seek to touch the sky and become immortal themselves. In the trees above, you observe the antics of squirrels and the busy chattering of many small animals, hardly distinguishable from this distance. The trail continues on to the south and to the east.",
          "grid_x": -2,
          "grid_y": -2,
          "exits": {
            "e": {
              "to_vnum": 3076,
              "to_zone": "Forest of Evermore",
