        "3081": {
          "vnum": 3081,
          "name": "The Forest of Evermore",
          "description": "Breaking the prolonged silence, a small furry creature slips from its precarious perch atop a tree and falls to the ground with a crash. Getting up hastily the creature dives from view into the bushes. A small path ends here leaving the only available exit to the southwest.",
