        "3082": {
          "vnum": 3082,
          "name": "A Shrouded Dell",
          "description": "Pine needles adorn the ground in profusion creating mysterious patterns that addle the mind. Even more strangely the pine needles have all fallen to the side of a worn trail leading further into the dell.",
