        "3084": {
          "vnum": 3084,
          "name": "Morelt Pool",
          "description": "Abruptly devoid of any trees, the area here opens up into a large clearing. The small path ends at the edge of an opaque pool of water that stretches across the entire clearing, ending in more pines. In the center of the pool a figure walks upon the water coming closer then fading into nothingness.",
