        "3086": {
          "vnum": 3086,
          "name": "An Opaque Pool",
          "description": "Within the pool it is extremely cold, sending shivers down your spine. The water is almost crystal clear here, despite the pool's opaque exterior. Fish shy cautiously away as you enter into their domain. Barely perceptible at the bottom of the pool lies the opening of a small tunnel.",
